---
title: Smoked Salmon Brunch Board with Pickled Onions and Dilly Cream Cheese
description: Spring is just around the corner and what better way to celebrate than with this plentiful brunch board! Complete with smoked salmon, pickled onions, dilly cream cheese and crisp veggies, this fresh and light spread is the perfect shareable meal.
